text: Anastasiya Romanivna Voznyak (; born 9 December 1998) is a Ukrainian female rhythmic gymnast. Voznyak competed alongside London 2012 Olympians Olena Dmytrash, Yevgeniya Gomon, Valeriia Gudym, and rookie Oleksandra Gridasova at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, where she and her Ukrainian team placed seventh in the group all-around final with a total score of 34.282. ==References== == External links == * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian rhythmic gymnasts Category:Sportspeople from Lviv Category:Gymnasts at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic gymnasts of Ukraine Category:European Games competitors for Ukraine Category:Gymnasts at the 2015 European Games Category:Gymnasts at the 2019 European Games Category:European Games medalists in gymnastics Category:European Games silver medalists for Ukraine Category:European Games bronze medalists for Ukraine Category:Universiade medalists in gymnastics Category:Universiade silver medalists for Ukraine Category:Medalists at the 2019 Summer Universiade
